{
  "texts": [
    "Another example is an autonomous car crashing into a wall to avoid a pedestrian.",
    "Insurance companies have other interests than the owner of the car or the developers of the software that steers the car's driving decisions.",
    "A final example is a denied bank loan: the bank and the client have different interests.",
    "In these cases, it might not be in the model user's best interest to look for the most correct or elaborate explanation of a decision that is made.",
    "The model user will most likely choose the explanation that fits their best interest, if diverse explanations are available."
  ]
}